    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >风暴海盗是一款回合制策略类roguelike游戏，致敬经典老牌游戏。它将你带入一个充满危险的海盗冒险世界。成为你自己船只的船长，招募船员，强化英雄，并探索那片不断改变你航线的神秘风暴。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070860/extras/fb0be7ab9b5bea48f790f790a6a3ab70.poster.avif?t=1747518047\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070860/extras/fb0be7ab9b5bea48f790f790a6a3ab70.webm?t=1747518047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070860/extras/fb0be7ab9b5bea48f790f790a6a3ab70.mp4?t=1747518047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典回合制策略，融合现代roguelike元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与海怪、敌对海盗和强大的首领展开战斗。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070860/extras/589d99ce9e28cf32422bb28367b8bcd7.poster.avif?t=1747518047\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070860/extras/589d99ce9e28cf32422bb28367b8bcd7.webm?t=1747518047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070860/extras/589d99ce9e28cf32422bb28367b8bcd7.mp4?t=1747518047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >航行在神秘莫测的海域，不断变化的世界等待探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每座岛屿都充满新的危险、任务和宝藏。程序化生成的岛屿、敌人和事件，让每一次旅程都独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募独特的船员，每位成员都有自己的技能与定位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从经验丰富的海盗到神秘的海洋生物，每个成员都至关重要！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次冒险，都是书写你传奇的机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好打破无尽的循环，成为史上最伟大的海盗了吗？</p>",
